			<ALIGNABLE_ANNOTATION ANNOTATION_ID="a328" TIME_SLOT_REF1="ts979" TIME_SLOT_REF2="ts982">
				<ANNOTATION_VALUE>er hot zikh farlibt fun di ERZSI, un zi, er hot zi gemakht oykh a MENAHELET. &lt;zi hot&gt; gornisht gearbet, nor a gantse tog &lt;hot zi&gt;</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
